tika.dc.description:
If you are an INTP, this book is an opportunity for you to learn from some of the most famous and successful people who share your personality type. Indulge yourself in this collection of over 200 fun, inspiring, and thought-provoking quotes from famous INTPs who share the same strengths and weaknesses as you do. Inside you'll find insights into relationships, creativity, work, happiness and money.

The quotes are broken into seven categories:

-Famous INTPs on Happiness and The Meaning of Life

-Famous INTPs on Family and Friends

-Famous INTPs on Business and Money

-Famous INTPs on Work, Career and Education

-Famous INTPs on Government and Religion

-Famous INTPs on Love, Relationships, Romance and Sex

-Famous INTPs on Healthy Living, Travel, Youth, and Everything Else

What better way to learn about success than from successful people who share your same core personality type?

Buy this book today for a thought provoking journey into your own personality...
